sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Platform Admin
    participant CLI as kubectl-odh
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant GH as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over User,K8s: Flow 1: Lint / Upgrade Readiness Assessment
        User->>CLI: kubectl odh lint [--checks=...] [--output=json]
        CLI->>K8s: GET DataScienceCluster (singleton)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC spec + status
        CLI->>K8s: GET DSCInitialization (singleton)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSCI spec + status
        CLI->>K8s: GET ClusterVersion<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: OpenShift version
        CLI->>K8s: LIST OLM Subscriptions, CSVs, PackageManifests<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Operator status + versions
        CLI->>K8s: LIST Notebooks, InferenceServices, ServingRuntimes,<br/>DSPA, RayClusters, PyTorchJobs, ClusterQueues,<br/>GuardrailsOrchestrators, LlamaStack, LLMInference<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Workload CRs (all namespaces)
        Note over CLI: Execute 37 checks across 5 groups<br/>(dependency, service, platform, component, workload)<br/>Version-gated: IsUpgradeFrom2xTo3x()
        CLI-->>User: DiagnosticResults<br/>(Prohibited > Blocking > Advisory > None)<br/>Table / JSON / YAML output
    end

    rect rgb(255, 249, 196)
        Note over User,FS: Flow 2: Backup Workloads
        User->>CLI: kubectl odh backup [--workload=notebooks] [--namespace=...]
        CLI->>K8s: LIST target workloads (Discovery Stage)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Workload resources
        par Dependency Resolution (concurrent workers)
            CLI->>K8s: GET ConfigMaps referenced by workloads<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8s-->>CLI: ConfigMap data
            CLI->>K8s: GET Secrets referenced by workloads<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8s-->>CLI: Secret data
            CLI->>K8s: GET PVCs referenced by workloads<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8s-->>CLI: PVC specs
        end
        Note over CLI: Notebook resolver: pod spec volumes + container env vars<br/>DSPA resolver: 9 JQ paths for storage/DB/CA/custom configs
        CLI->>FS: Write YAML files (workloads + dependencies)
        CLI-->>User: Backup complete (file paths listed)
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over User,K8s: Flow 3: Migration (Kueue → RHBOK)
        User->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate prepare --action=kueue-rhbok
        CLI->>K8s: LIST ClusterQueues, LocalQueues, ConfigMaps<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Current Kueue resources
        CLI->>FS: Write backup YAML (ClusterQueues, ConfigMaps)
        CLI-->>User: Prepare complete (backup files written)

        User->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate run --action=kueue-rhbok [--dry-run]
        CLI->>K8s: CREATE OLM Subscription (RHBOK operator)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Subscription created
        CLI->>K8s: PATCH ConfigMaps (prevent DSC reconciliation)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: ConfigMaps annotated
        CLI->>K8s: PATCH DataScienceCluster (managementState)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC updated
        CLI->>K8s: LIST ClusterQueues, LocalQueues (verify preserved)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Resources verified intact
        CLI-->>User: Migration complete (StepRecorder tree output)
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over User,GH: Flow 4: Dependency Check (with optional refresh)
        User->>CLI: kubectl odh deps [--refresh]
        opt --refresh flag
            CLI->>GH: GET raw.githubusercontent.com/odh-gitops/.../values.yaml<br/>No Auth (public)
            GH-->>CLI: Dependency manifest YAML
        end
        Note over CLI: Parse embedded or fetched manifest<br/>(go:embed from odh-gitops pinned commit)
        CLI->>K8s: LIST OLM Subscriptions + Deployments<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Installed operator state
        Note over CLI: Compare required vs. installed dependencies
        CLI-->>User: Dependency status table (installed / missing / version mismatch)
    end
